name: Acerca de lo que no se dice
description:
"About what is not said"

This is another piece from the Mutations series. I think it is the most "literal" one I painted that time and it showed many of my feelings, or sensations. I always thought that my skin, the boundary with the outside, was the most sensitive barrier I had, turning the wound into a direct path to my inside.

Oil on canvas

Dimensions: 2454 px x 3163 px
Size: 60 x 80 cm
